# Ticket ID: TICKET-020

## Issue Title
User Unable to Connect to VPN

## Description
A remote user reported that they were unable to establish a VPN connection due to authentication failure.

## Initial Checks
- Verified internet connectivity
- Checked VPN client status

## Troubleshooting Performed
- Verified user credentials
- Checked VPN account validity
- Reset VPN credentials

## Root Cause
VPN credentials had expired.

## Resolution
Updated the userâ€™s VPN credentials. The user successfully established a VPN connection afterward.